---
title: Chicken Parmigiana with Fresh Mozzarella  Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Skip right over the time consuming what-to-make-for-dinner debate, and jump right into this quick-cooking, stress-free chicken dinner that’s on the table in 15 minutes. All you have to do is boil water for spinach-ricotta ravioli that you’ll toss with luscious garlic-herb butter, sizzle up juicy chicken cutlets with melty fresh mozzarella on top, and whip up a speedy marinara-scallion-herb sauce in the same pan. Sprinkle it all with crispy fried onions, and just like that, you’re a kitchen hero.
